  "description": "<p><strong>The Hackable Assets Roll Table </strong>has been created to enable the unprepared or improvising cyberpunk GM to generate net-linked assets in the PC’s vicinity, quickly and easily, simply by rolling some dice.</p><p></p><p>Roll 4-5 times on the table to tell you the type of systems your players have in their proximity.</p><p>Roll the same number of D10s. e used in different ways; to determine the relative security levels on a scale of 1 (no security) to 10 (killer ICE), as the target inked systems are connected to the first, or how many rounds before a sysadmin notices any spurious activity on their network.</p><p>To ascertain if nearby the system has any quirks or notable features, roll D100 on the @UUID[Compendium.augmented-reality-foundry.augmentedrealityrolltables.RollTable.drJSk7wxiPWrYr1s]{Bugs In The System} table.</p>",
